Package de.lmu.ifi.mfa

The package provides a model of a flow network in the FlowNetwork class as an implementation of the interface IFlowNetwork.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IFlowNetwork
    The IFlowNetwork interface represents a flow network consisting of a directed graph of vertices.
    IGraph
    The IGraph interface represents a directed graph that can be used to implement a flow network.

Package de.lmu.ifi.mfa Description

The package provides a model of a flow network in the FlowNetwork class as an implementation of the interface IFlowNetwork. It supports the following two primary functionalities: create and manipulate a flow network, evaluate the maximum flow on the network.

For additional information, see MFA project by Christian Gebhardt on Github.
